    "body": "Just to confirm here, the issue does seem to be related to pnpm not installing peer dependencies automatically. I had the same issue as OP when creating a new Hardhat project, with ethers.getSigners imported as { ethers } from \"hardhat\". \r\n\r\nI nuked my node_modules and reinstalled with npm (v9) and the issue disappeared. There are ways to tell pnpm to auto-install peer dependencies but it might be best just to stick with npm. ",
